Requirements

API Information
Url: darksky.net
Documentation: https://darksky.net/dev/docs
API Key: 47dd4c596abbfb16bc6bd4be0ed3c661

Description: The same API that powers Forecast.io and Dark Sky for iOS can provide
accurate short-term and long-term weather predictions to your
business, application, or crazy idea.
Design an application that will report following weather statistics:
● Current Weather
● Upcoming Weather (Next Hour)
● Tomorrow’s Weather
● Next 7 Days Weather (Aggregate)
● Five Day Forecast
c. Bonus
● You should be able to filter weather forecasts by City, State
● Include weather icons for each forecast
● Make the layout a responsive design
